videos.description: Maya Dodson scores on consecutive possessions to put Notre Dame ahead of NC State.

videos.description: Notre Dame freshman Sonia Citron comes up with a steal on defense and passes ahead to Olivia Miles for a transition layup.

videos.description: NC State gets two open looks to tie the game in the final seconds, but both are off the mark, and Notre Dame hangs on for the upset win.
